Examples:

@c ===beg===
@c load ("lbfgs");
@c load ("augmented_lagrangian");
@c FOM: x^2 + 2*y^2;
@c xx: [x, y];
@c C: [x + y - 1];
@c yy: [1, 1];
@c augmented_lagrangian_method(FOM, xx, C, yy, iprint=[-1,0]);
@c ===end===
